Loading DA has nothing to do with the discussion on loading Gate. We do get 8 spell slots. We can load both. I always have, they are both loaded at this moment indeed. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
DA is the second best spell we clerics ever get (after Complete Heal). Whilst there are now (at level 60) occasions when I do drop Gate (ie big raid situations where it would never be used), I never drop DA at all. DA/Gate together make a great cleric survival kit. If this means you need to swap in/out other spells on occasions, do it with less vital ones.<br>
<br>
